27static const int CODE_WIDTH = 3 + // start guard
28 (7 * 4) + // left bars
29 5 + // middle guard
30 (7 * 4) + // right bars
31 3; // end guard

33BitMatrix
34EAN8Writer::encode(const std::wstring& contents, int width, int height) const
35{
36 auto digits = UPCEANCommon::DigitString2IntArray<8>(contents);
37
38 std::vector<bool> result(CODE_WIDTH, false);
39 int pos = 0;
40
41 pos += WriterHelper::AppendPattern(result, pos, UPCEANCommon::START_END_PATTERN, true);
42
43 for (int i = 0; i <= 3; i++) {
44 pos += WriterHelper::AppendPattern(result, pos, UPCEANCommon::L_PATTERNS[digits[i]], false);
45 }
46
47 pos += WriterHelper::AppendPattern(result, pos, UPCEANCommon::MIDDLE_PATTERN, false);
48
49 for (int i = 4; i <= 7; i++) {
50 pos += WriterHelper::AppendPattern(result, pos, UPCEANCommon::L_PATTERNS[digits[i]], true);
51 }
52 WriterHelper::AppendPattern(result, pos, UPCEANCommon::START_END_PATTERN, true);
53 return WriterHelper::RenderResult(result, width, height, _sidesMargin >= 0 ? _sidesMargin : 9);
54}
